Police in Mdantsane have arrested a 21-year-old man for fraud and impersonating a lawyer today. The suspect allegedly defrauded people of thousands of rands in Willowvale and East London, pretending to be the son and partner of a well-known advocate, Dali Mpofu.The victims alerted the police and an operation was conducted swiftly. The suspect was arrested in Mdantsane and was found to be in possession of a replica gown for lawyers and fraudulent documents written byAdvocate Dali Mpofu&#8217;s law firm.The suspect is due to appear in the Mdantsane Magistrate s Court soon, facing charges of fraud and impersonating a lawyer.